tiers.ability_description:
At the start of battle, Jawa allies gain 100% bonus Protection until the end of the encounter and all enemies are inflicted with Provoked for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted. Whenever a Jawa ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Jawa allies gain Foresight for 1 turn. Whenever an enemy is inflicted with Thermal Detonators, Jawa allies gain 10% Defense and Offense (stacking, max 300%). At the start of each turn, if a Jawa ally has 50% or less Health, damage they receive is reduced by 75% (excluding percent health damage and massive damage) until the end of the turn.

Whenever an enemy takes damage from a Thermal Detonator expiring, which can't be evaded, Jawa allies recover 5% Health and Protection, gain 5% Turn Meter, and that enemy is inflicted with an aditional Thermal Detonator for 1 turn, which can't be dispelled, evaded, or resisted.

Whenever Chief Nebit calls allies to assist, he recovers 10% Health and Protection for each ally that assists, and other Jawa allies recover 5% Health and Protection.
Whenever an enemy is inflicted with Thermal Detonator, there is a 50% chance to inflict an additional Thermal Detonator for 2 turns.
Light Side allies have +100% Critical Chance while attacking out of turn.
At the start of each Rogue One ally's turn, if they have not taken damage since their last turn, they gain Critical Chance Up and Offense Up for 1 turn.
Whenever Jyn Erso critically hits an enemy, Jyn Erso gains 10% Critical Damage, Defense Penetration, and Offense (stacking, max 200%) until the end of battle.
At the start of the encounter Dark Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Dark Side ally.
Whenever an enemy is defeated by a First Order ally, that enemy can't be revived.

First Order SF TIE Pilot has +100% Potency. While allied Supreme Leader Kylo Ren is active, First Order SF TIE Pilot can't be defeated. While First Order allies have Advantage, they ignore Taunt.

Whenever the ally in the Leader slot or First Order SF TIE Pilot is damaged while they have Advantage, Stun that enemy for 1 turn, which can't be resisted. Whenever an enemy is Stunned, First Order SF TIE Pilot's abilities gain 5% bonus damage (stacking, max 200%), he and the ally in the Leader slot gain 10% Max Health until the end of the encounter, and if the ally in the Leader slot is Supreme Leader Kylo Ren, he gains 5% Ultimate Charge. Whenever a Stunned enemy is defeated, they can't be revived, the ally in the Leader slot gains a bonus turn, and the allied Leader and First Order SF TIE Pilot recover 100% Health and Protection.
Whenever Dark Side allies evade an attack, they gain Offense Up for 1 turn.
The first time each Light Side ally is defeated, remaining Light Side allies gain 15% Offense and 20 Speed (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.
Whenever a Unaligned Force User ally deals damage to an enemy and no other enemy is Ability Blocked, inflict Ability Block for 1 turn on the target enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.
The first time each turn Rey gains Ultimate Charge, they gain an additional 6% Ultimate Charge.
Whenever Light Side allies are evaded by an enemy, that ally gains Accuracy Up for 2 turns, and they inflict Evasion Down for 2 turns on that enemy, which can't be evaded.
Whenever Dark Side allies evade an attack, they gain Offense Up for 1 turn.
At the beginning of their turn, Light Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all debuffs on themself.
At the beginning of their turn, Light Side allies have +25% chance to dispel all debuffs on themself.
Whenever Light Side allies are evaded by an enemy, that ally gains Accuracy Up for 2 turns, and they inflict Evasion Down for 2 turns on that enemy, which can't be evaded.
Whenever Light Side allies use a Special ability, they gain Evasion Up, Health Steal Up, and Health Up  for 2 turns.

Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User critically hits an enemy, dispel all debuffs on themself and gain 5% Turn Meter. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability against an enemy with at least 3 debuffs, reduce that enemy's Max Health by 5%. Whenever a Dark Side or Light Side Unaligned Force User uses a Special ability when they have at least 3 buffs that can be dispelled, gain 5% Max Health.

Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker damages an enemy with a Special ability and the enemy doesn't have Armor Shred, inflict Armor Shred on them for the rest of the battle. Whenever Commander Luke Skywalker uses a Basic ability and damages an enemy with Armor Shred, inflict Expose for 2 turns, which can't be resisted, and Commander Luke Skywalker gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns.
Whenever Dark Side allies gain Tenacity Up, they gain Protection Up (10%, stacking) for 2 turns.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.
The first time each Tank ally falls below 50% Health they gain Damage Immunity for 1 turn and gain Health Steal Up for 2 turns.

If Chirrut Îmwe is an ally, then whenever Baze Malbus or Chirrut Îmwe attacks out of turn, they gain 50% Critical Chance and equalize their Health and Protection.

While attacking out of turn, if Baze Malbus or Chirrut Îmwe scores a critical hit, they both recover 10% Health and Protection. If Baze Malbus has less than 50% Health, whenever he takes damage, the weakest enemy is dealt 100% of that damage, which can't defeat them.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.

Whenever an ally inflicts a debuff on an enemy, all Attacker allies gain Accuracy Up for 1 turn and 5% Offense (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle. Whenever an Attacker attacks out of turn, they deal bonus True damage, which can't be evaded, and gain 5% Defense Penetration (stacking, max 120%) until the end of battle.

Whenever Attacker uses a Special ability, deal 25% more damage for each buff on target enemy.

During Attacker's turn, they ignore Stealth and Taunt if they have no debuff on them.
Whenever Lando Calrissian scores a critical hit, bonus damage for Double Down is increased by 25% (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.
Dark Side allies start the battle with Protection Up (20%) for 2 turns.

Whenever Healer allies recover Health, they recover Protection equal to the amount of Health recovered. Healer allies can't recover Protection this way more than once per turn or if their Health was full.
Whenever another ally is defeated, Old Daka takes a bonus turn and their cooldowns are reset.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.

Whenever CT-5555 "Fives" attacks out of turn, CT-5555 "Fives" deals 150% bonus damage, inflicts Offense Down and Healing Immunity for 1 turn on all enemies, which can't be evaded or resisted.
Whenever CT-5555 "Fives" loses Taunt, he removes 50% Turn Meter from all enemies and inflicts Blind on them for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever Thrawn resists a debuff, all allies recover 10% Health and Protection, and gain 20% Health Steal (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever Thrawn attacks out of turn, he ignores Protection, and if the enemy is inflicted with Burning, Thrawn deals 100% bonus damage and removes 100% Turn Meter, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever R2-D2 uses a Basic ability, R2-D2 gains Protection Up (50%, stacking) for 2 turns and 50% Turn Meter. Whenever R2-D2 damages an enemy using a Special ability, inflict Fear for 1 turn on that enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted.

At the start of each encounter, if there is another Support ally, Darth Nihilus gains 100% Max Health and Max Protection for the rest of the encounter.

Whenever Darth Nihilus reduces his cooldowns, for each cooldown reduced, he gains 25% Turn Meter and 50% Offense (stacking) for the rest of the encounter.

Whenever Darth Nihilus defeats an enemy, Expose all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.

Whenever Darth Nihilus inflicts Damage Over Time on an enemy, all allies gain 3 stacks of Heal Over Time for 2 turns.

Whenever Darth Nihilus attacks out of turn, his cooldown for Annihilate reduces by 1.

Each time Poggle the Lesser inflicts Ability Block, he also inflicts Burning for 2 turns on the target enemy, Poggle the Lesser gains 10% Turn Meter, and all allies gain 20% Offense (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever IG-86 critically hits an enemy, IG-86 gains Damage Immunity for 1 turn, 25% Turn Meter, and inflicts Deathmark on the target enemy for 2 turns, which can't be dispelled, evaded, or resisted. If the enemy was already Deathmarked, IG-86 gains Protection Up (50%, stacking), Retribution, and Speed Up for 2 turns.

If HK-47 is in the Leader slot, whenever an ally damages an enemy with Ability Block or Fear, IG-88 assists, Shocks that enemy, which can't be evaded or resisted, and inflicts them with Torture for 1 turn, which can't be copied, dispelled, evaded, or resisted, and all allies gain Offense Up for 2 turns.

At the start of each encounter, Poe inflicts Fear on all enemies, which can't be copied, dispelled, evaded, prevented, or resisted, and Exposes them for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted. Whenever Taunt expires on Poe, all enemies are inflicted with Fear for 1 turn, which can't be copied or dispelled, and all allies gain 20% Turn Meter. Whenever Poe Dameron is critically hit while Taunting, he gains Protection Up (50%) for 1 turn. Whenever a buff expires on another ally, Poe Taunts for 1 turn.
Whenever Light Side allies start their turn with at least 2 buffs that can be dispelled, they gain 5% Offense (stacking) until the end of the encounter.
Whenever Dark Side allies are evaded by an enemy, that ally gains Accuracy Up for 2 turns, and they inflict Evasion Down for 2 turns on that enemy, which can't be evaded.
Whenever Attacker allies use a Special Ability on their turn, they gain Riposte for 2 turns.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.
At the start of the encounter Light Side allies gain 15% Max Health and Max Protection for each other Light Side ally.

The first time a Tank ally is defeated, revive them with 100% Health and Protection, and they gain a bonus turn. Limit once per battle.

Tank allies Taunt for 1 turn, whenever another ally is inflicted with a debuff. Whenever Tank allies Taunt, they gain Defense Up for 1 turn and 5% Crit Avoidance (stacking) until the end of battle.

Whenever a Tank is critically hit while Taunting, they recover 15% Health and Protection. Whenever a non-tank ally uses a Special ability, Tank allies assist, if the enemy was Taunting, deal 250% bonus damage.

At the start of each encounter, Dengar inflicts Doubt on all enemies for 2 turns, which can't be evaded, dispelled, or resisted.

Whenever an enemy evades Dengar's attack or resists a debuff, all enemies are inflicted with a stack of Damage Over Time and Thermal Detonator for 2 turns, which can't be evaded or resisted.
